{
  "id": "adv_bond_szk_01_02",
  "title": "兵藤雫2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "じゃあ私のスマホで撮影お願い……！\nどう……？　ちゃんとカメラ……映ってる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ please take a video with my smartphone…!\nHow is it…? Is it properly reflected… on the camera…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　ばっちりだよ！　あれ……雫ちゃん……\nちょっと肌荒れてる？　ほっぺにニキビ出来てるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Perfect! Oh… Shizuku-chan…\nIs your skin a little rough? You have a pimple on your cheek!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、私の顔をアップで撮ってる……！？\n違う……顔のアップはいらない……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ are you taking a close-up video of my face…!?\nThat's wrong… No need to close-up in on face…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4999997457,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "手元が映るように……\nもう少し引いてくれると……嬉しい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that the hands can be seen…\nIf you could pull it off a little more… I'd be happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "配信のメインは……私じゃない……お魚……\nもはや私の顔は切れててもいい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The main of the show is… not me… it's fish…\nIt's okay if my face doesn't show anymore…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.5999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　そうだった！　ごめんね！　もう少し引いて……\n雫ちゃんの全身が入るようにっと。よし、OKだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah! That's right! Sorry! Pull back a little more…\nSo that Shizuku-chan's entire body can fit in it. Good‚ that's OK!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう……それじゃあ……配信スタート……！\nみなさん、こんにちは……サニーピースの兵藤雫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you… Then… Broadcasting start…!\nHello‚ everyone… I'm Shizuku Hyodo from Sunny Peace",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.0666671753,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……大好きな釣りとお魚の魅力を伝えるため……\n雫fishチャンネルを……開設しました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… to deliver the charm of fishing and fish that I love…\nShizuku fish channel… has been opened…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.5999994914,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "よっ！　雫ちゃん！　どんどん伝えちゃって！\nせっかくだし、これも被ってみようか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yo! Shizuku-chan! Tell us more!\nTaking this opportunity‚ let's try this‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.5666692098,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6533.331807500005
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.333333399997
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 9233.3307902
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 11199.997456900008
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さくらちゃん……！？　配信中……！\nカメラ持って近づいてこないで……わぁ～～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sakura-chan…!? On air…!\nDon't come near me with a camera… wahh~~…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.8000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk008.m4a",
      "text": "カメラマンが被せてくれました……え……カンペ……？\n「いつも私のそばにぎょぎょっと、ぎょぎょっと」？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cameraman put it on… eh… a cue card…?\n'Always by my side‚ Gyogyo-tto‚ Gyogyo-tto'?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8999994915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk009.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ早速……今日は……じゃーん……！\n朝から私が釣ってきた……このブリを捌く……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ right away… today is… ta-daー…!\nI'm going to clean this yellowtail… I caught this morning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.2333435059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ～！　すっごく大きい！\n雫ちゃんの半分くらいの大きさはあるよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow~! It's so big!\nIt's about half size of Shizuku~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7666768392,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk010.m4a",
      "text": "ブリは縁起のいい魚……きっとこの配信もうまくいく\n捌き方は……遙子さんに習ったからばっちり……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yellowtail is a lucky fish… I'm sure this show will go well\nHow to clean fish… I learned it from Haruko-san‚ so it's perfect…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6666768392,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11599.991862100012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk011.m4a",
      "text": "ウロコはもう落としてある……いざ、入刀……！\nまずはエラ蓋をこじ開けて……内臓を……グイっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Scales have already been removed… Now‚ cutting…!\nFirst‚ pry open the gill cover… and the innards… swish",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4333424886,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "きゃーっ！　凄い凄い！　お魚さんの中身がどんどん\n出てくる～！　私のお腹もぎょ～ってなってきたよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wowー! Awesome‚ awesome! Fish-san's insides are coming out\nmore and more~! ! My stomach is going Gyo~‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.566675822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk012.m4a",
      "text": "まさか内臓のアップにしてる……？　ファンもビックリ\nする……内臓じゃなくて胴体……ブリを映して！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you close-up the innards…? Fans will be\nsuprised… not innards‚ but trunk… Show yellowtail!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.9000132243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ごめんごめん！\nはいっ、ちゃんとブリにカメラ戻しました！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry sorry!\nOkay‚ I managed to return the camera to yellowtail!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.3000162761,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk013.m4a",
      "text": "ほっ……次に両側から背骨の付け根を切って頭を\n落とす……ここからは三枚おろしの手順で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Next‚ cut the base of the spine on both sides and cut\nthe head… From here‚ follow the steps to fillet it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.5000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "お魚さんのお顔って可愛いな～！　唇がプルプルしてて\nキュート！　雫ちゃん、あとでお顔だけちょーだい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fish-san's face is so cute~! His lips are so plump\nand cute! Shizuku-chan‚ give me this face laterー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 174.2000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_szk_01_02-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん……！　お魚のお顔はいいから……胴体！\nブリを……映して……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan…! Fish's face is fine… trunk!\nShowing… yellowtail…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.4000061035,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}